{"id": 469, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的人生有过哪些错觉？", "description": "全都是泡沫。", "record_count": 8865, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145056WG0FwvkfVDqMxKA4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-10T10:47:39Z", "options": [{"id": 7681, "content": "我瘦了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157937}, {"id": 7682, "content": "今天换了件新衣服，感觉周围的人都在看…", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211125CAgtYaPWX76F3m2n.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157934}, {"id": 8706, "content": "再睡5分钟我就醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166510}, {"id": 7683, "content": "睡死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157987}, {"id": 7685, "content": "煤气没关 门没关 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157761}, {"id": 7686, "content": "我能吃完", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158276}, {"id": 7688, "content": "洗了个澡就变漂亮或者是帅了！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157098}, {"id": 7689, "content": "面前发生的事我似乎梦到过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156652}, {"id": 8202, "content": "我现在不完美很幼稚，是因为我还年轻不成熟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161219}, {"id": 8714, "content": "他们在打龙！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166641}, {"id": 18700, "content": "喜欢了一个世纪的女生，她喜欢我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 48653, "content": "最近不知怎么了，一听到人家说话声稍小一点，就觉得他在说英语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464152}, {"id": 8464, "content": "这个点出门还来得及", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164191}, {"id": 13074, "content": "我喜欢他", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235039tYN97XlkB04D21ng.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201385}, {"id": 8217, "content": "跟他拼！我能反杀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161686}, {"id": 10009, "content": "我是个人妖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172585}, {"id": 8740, "content": "万事万物都能朝我想要的方向去发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166935}, {"id": 7975, "content": "有人叫我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159862}, {"id": 8745, "content": "他还喜欢我，他只喜欢我", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234911OSGlbqWCe6wrdci7.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166990}, {"id": 8492, "content": "他们好像在讨论我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164364}, {"id": 8493, "content": "觉得这次考得不错，特别好，一定能过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164346}, {"id": 10029, "content": "我是?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157295}, {"id": 8238, "content": "以为自己已经脱离梦境", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161034}, {"id": 7732, "content": "这个月工资应该不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157470}, {"id": 8252, "content": "我可以的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159579}, {"id": 10044, "content": "考试之前：复习好了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172256}, {"id": 8253, "content": "我可以的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159579}, {"id": 7998, "content": "我瘦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159936}, {"id": 8000, "content": "先玩会儿，一会儿在看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157432}, {"id": 8001, "content": "我还可以再拼搏下去…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159950}, {"id": 7748, "content": "我有意见，你们都把我的错觉说完了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158636}, {"id": 7237, "content": "他喜欢我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 968, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7238, "content": "手机在震动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 819, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7239, "content": "我可以反杀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 297, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8007, "content": "我没吃过饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 61819}, {"id": 7240, "content": "差距不大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 546, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7752, "content": "以为能反杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155273}, {"id": 7241, "content": "别人点赞=别人喜欢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 369, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 13897, "content": "不写作业会死…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213106}, {"id": 7242, "content": "我“果取关”别人就会“伤欲绝”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8266, "content": "我的人参都是错觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131040}, {"id": 7759, "content": "爸妈很相爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155086}, {"id": 8273, "content": "我可以的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159579}, {"id": 8277, "content": "1.他喜欢我   2.这把能赢   3.我能反杀   4.他们在看我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42858}, {"id": 7770, "content": "以为他在看我", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158683}, {"id": 7516, "content": "我觉得我还可以再抢救一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149593}, {"id": 7517, "content": "手机响了，是她的信息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 403, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146167}, {"id": 8285, "content": "别人是不是学习的时间比我多啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 45405, "content": "我一定不会在拿起手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149313}, {"id": 7518, "content": "好像没吃饱", "image": null, "praise_count": 195, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}]}